湖北电影厂员工一家四口接连去世  新冠家庭死亡率高企需关注。
The death rate of four family members in Hubei Film Factory is very high.
2020-02-16 20:40:40来源： 财新网作者：萧辉 包志明责任编辑：高昱。
2020-02-16 20: 40: 40 Source: Caixin Network Author: Xiaohui Bao Zhiming Responsibility Editor: Gao yu.
2020年02月16日 20:40。
16 February 2020 at 20: 40.
来源于。
From sources.
财新网。
Caixin Net.
可以听文章啦！。
Listen to the passage.
在家隔离致病情拖延得不到有效救治，是新冠肺炎家庭聚集性传染和轻症发展成重症的主要原因，但有些家庭的重症率和死亡率明显偏高。
The main causes of serious illness are familial clustered infections and mild cases of Newly Coronary Pneumonia, but some families have significantly higher rates of severe illness and death.
专家认为这或许跟新冠病毒与某些特定基因或者体内菌群“更为亲和”有关，建议加强病理学检验。
Experts believe it may be linked to a new crown virus being "more compatible" with certain genes or bacterial flora in the body, suggesting stronger pathology tests.
2月2日，武汉市中心医院，门诊大厅门外的患者。
February 2, Wuhan City Central Hospital, out-patient hall outside the patients.
自1月23日交通封城以来，因为医院床位严重短缺，武汉大量病人无法确诊、住院。
Since the closure of the city on January 23, a large number of Wuhan patients could not be diagnosed and hospitalized because of a severe shortage of hospital beds.
早期对疑似病例疏于管理的驼鸟政策，造成了多重问题。
Early camel-bird policies that were poorly managed for suspected cases caused multiple problems.
图/财新记者 丁刚。
Photo / Finance new reporter Ding Gang.
相关报道2月15日：全国新冠肺炎累计确诊68500例 死亡1665例武汉病毒所：网传新冠“零号病人”是该所学生消息不实武汉仍有少量新冠病人未入院 隔离点治疗能力不足需重视肺炎日记|2月15日：极端雨雪冲击武汉，医疗增援远超汶川新冠肺炎“吹哨人”李文亮：真相最重要。
Wuhan has a small number of newly-westbound patients with unhospitalized isolation. Wuhan still has a small number of newly westbound patients with unhospitalized isolation sites. Pneumonia has been hit by severe rain and snow that hit Wuhan Feb. 15, 2007.
【财新网】（记者 萧辉 包志明）正与疫情艰难抗战的武汉，又添一起一家多人感染新冠肺炎去世的悲剧。
Journalist Xiaohui Bao Zhiming is in the midst of a tough fight against the epidemic in Wuhan, adding to the tragic death of a family with a new crown pneumonia.
湖北省电影制片厂2月14日发出讣告，其“像音像”对外联络部主任常凯因患新冠肺炎医治无效，于当日凌晨4时51分在武汉市黄陂人民医院逝世，享年55岁。
Hubei Film Studios issued an obituary on Feb. 14. Changkai, director of the "audio-visual" communication department for foreign affairs, died at 4: 51 am of the same day at Wuhan Huangpi People's Hospital, aged 55.
。
.
财新记者从常凯大学同学处获悉，常凯的父亲、母亲和他的姐姐在半个多月里也陆续患新冠肺炎离世，其同样感染新冠肺炎的妻子目前正在重症监护室（ICU）抢救中。
Changkai's father, mother and sister died of pneumonia more than half a month later, and his wife, who also contracted pneumonia, is in intensive care unit (ICU), said the reporter.
。
.
据常凯的同学介绍，常凯夫妻和父母住在盘龙城小区，1月24日除夕夜，常凯在家中掌勺和父母一起吃团年饭。
Changkai's classmates said the couple and their parents lived in the area of Panlong City. On January 24, Changkai ate a reunion dinner with his parents at home on New Year's Eve.
1月25日，常凯父亲出现新冠肺炎感染症状，发烧咳嗽，呼吸困难，送至多家医院，均被告知没有床位接收。
On January 25, Changkai's father developed symptoms of pneumonia, fever, cough, breathing difficulties, sent to a number of hospitals, were told no bed reception.
常凯无奈只能将父亲接回家，由他和姐姐一起照顾。
Changkai can only take his father home, by him and his sister together care.
但三天后，常凯父亲即很快离世。
But three days later, Changkai's father died soon after.
2月2日，常凯的母亲亦因新冠肺炎去世。
On February 2, Changkai's mother also died of pneumonia.
2月14日凌晨，常凯因新冠肺炎去世，紧接着当天下午，常凯姐姐也因新冠肺炎去世。
In the early hours of February 14, Changkai died of pneumonia, immediately following the afternoon of the same day, Changkai sister died of pneumonia.
目前，常凯的妻子正在重症监护室抢救。
Changkai's wife is currently in intensive care unit rescue.
17天，一家四口居家传染新冠病毒，相继离世，朋友为此难过唏嘘不已。
Seventeen days, a family of four people infected with the new crown virus, died one after another, friends for this sad.
。
.
常凯的大学同学证实，常凯在去世前写了一段遗言，讲述求医之艰难：“大年初一，老爷子发烧咳嗽，呼吸困难，送至多家医院就治，均告无床位接收，多方求助，也还是一床难求。
Changkai's college classmates confirmed that Changkai wrote a suicide note before his death about the difficulty of seeking medical treatment. "On the first day of the New Year, the old man had a fever, coughed and breathed difficulties.
失望之及，回家自救，床前尽孝，寥寥数日，回天乏术，老父含恨撒手人寰，多重打击之下，慈母身心疲惫，免疫力尽失，亦遭烈性感染，随老父而去。
Disappointed, he went home to help himself, a few days before the bed, very few days, the old father hateful to die, under multiple blows, mother tired, immune, also suffered from strong infection, with the old father left.
床前服侍双亲数日，无情冠状病毒也吞噬了爱妻和我的躯体。
Beside his parents for several days, the heartless coronavirus devoured my wife and my body.
辗转诸家医院哀求哭拜，怎奈位卑言轻，床位难觅，直至病入膏肓，错失医治良机，奄奄气息之中，广告亲朋好友及远在英伦吾儿：我一生为子尽孝，为父尽责，为夫爱妻，为人尽诚！永别了！我爱的人和爱我的人。
Through hospitals cry and pray, How can I be humble, bed hard to find Until the terminally ill, When I miss my chance to heal, And in the midst of the elections, Amid all the years I have spent my life filial piety, fatherly duty, loving wife and devotion! Farewell!
”。
"
常凯出生于1964年，1989年进入武汉大学新闻系摄影专业学习。
Changkai was born in 1964, in 1989 into Wuhan University Department of Journalism major study.
他的同学称，大学时期的常凯一头飘逸的长发，很有才气，为人随和，享有才子美誉，毕业后进入湖北省电影制片厂。
His classmates said Changkai had long flowing hair, was talented, easy-going, enjoyed a reputation as a talented person, and went to the Hubei Film Studios after graduation.
湖北省电影制片厂的讣告称，常凯自参加工作以来，一贯爱岗敬业，积极肯干，工作作风踏实，在历任岗位上作出了重要贡献，曾多次被评为湖北电影制片厂标兵、先进工作者。
Since joining the film studio in Hubei Province, Changkai has always loved his work, been willing to work actively and conscientiously, and has made important contributions to various posts. He has been voted the standard-bearer and advanced worker of Hubei Film Studio on many occasions.
他对人和善，乐于助人，深受职工的尊敬和好评。
He is kind and helpful and is highly respected and praised by his staff.
。
.
“常凯是那么善良随和的一个人，一家四口就突然离开了，我们大学同学很难接受。
"Changkai is such a kind and easy-going person, a family of four suddenly left, our college students find it difficult to accept.
希望这样的惨剧能让人知道，并被追问，这到底是谁的过错。
It is hoped that such a tragedy can be known and questioned, this is whose fault.
”常凯的大学同学说。
"said Changkai's college classmates.
。
.
自1月23日交通封城以来，因为医院床位严重短缺，武汉大量病人无法确诊、住院。
Since the closure of the city on January 23, a large number of Wuhan patients could not be diagnosed and hospitalized because of a severe shortage of hospital beds.
早期对疑似病例疏于管理的驼鸟政策，造成了多重问题。
Early camel-bird policies that were poorly managed for suspected cases caused multiple problems.
其一，患者得不到及时诊断，无法及早治疗阻断病程，导致快速发展成重症、危重症，极大提高了致死率；其二，大部分疑似病人无法入院隔离，只能在家等待床位，家庭性传染和社区性传染等聚集性传播持续，形成规模更为可怕的新增病例；其三，疑似病人发展到重症、危重症后，会出现呼吸衰竭等无法自抑的症状，必须到医院进行医学处置，不得不来回于居住地和多家医院排队挂号、输液以及等待核酸试剂盒检测和入院，导致更多交叉感染。
Second, most of the suspected patients cannot be hospitalized and can only wait for bed at home. Third, the suspected patients will continue to accumulate sexually transmitted diseases, such as respiratory failure, to the hospital for medical treatment, and have to wait for nucleic acid test kits for testing and admission.
财新记者在前线获悉的患者无法就医，从轻症拖延成了重症再到危重症，高烧不退、呼吸衰竭进而病死家中，甚至一家多人患病几至灭门的惨剧都不是一例两例。
There are no cases of patients reported to the front-line by financial journalists, ranging from mild to severe illness, high fever, respiratory failure and death, or even the near-total death of a single family.
。
.
值得注意的是，尽管医学界认为新冠病毒对各年龄段人的易感性并无多大差别，在家隔离和病情拖延得不到有效医学干预，也是导致家庭聚集性传染和轻症患者发展成重症的主要原因，但根据财新记者对多名一线重症治疗专家的采访，新冠肺炎轻症发展成重症的平均比率在15%-20%，而有些家庭的重症率和死亡率明显偏高。
It is worth noting that, while the medical community does not consider the prevalence of the new crown virus to be significantly different for all age groups, home isolation and delayed access to effective medical intervention are also the main causes of family-focused sexually transmitted infections and mild illness. However, according to interviews with leading specialists in frontline intensive care, the average progression from mild to severe coronary pneumonia ranges from 15% to 20%.
一位上海援鄂医疗队的专家对财新记者表示，这或许跟新冠病毒与某些特定基因或者体内菌群“更为亲和”有关，他建议加强病理学检验，帮助科研人员加快新冠肺炎患者病理改变和疾病机制等相关研究。
An expert from the medical team in Shanghai told reporters that it may be linked to the new crown virus being "more compatible" with certain genes or bacteria in the body, and suggested strengthening pathology tests to help researchers speed up research on pathologic changes and disease mechanisms in patients with new crowns pneumonia.
。
.
